---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base>
	<section class="bgImg dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 h-40 w-full">
		<div class="overlay1 w-full"></div>
	</section>


	<section class="bg-[#001822] dark:bg-gray-900 py-2 px-4 mx-auto lg:py-2 lg:px-6">
		<div class="">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-screen-md text-center mb-8 lg:mb-12">
				<p class="text-[#ea580c] text-sm mb-4">PRICING SECTION</p>
				<h2 class="mb-4 text-2xl tracking-tight font-normal text-gray-100 uppercase">Pick the price thats right for you</h2>
				<p class="mb-5 font-light text-sm text-gray-200">Join millions of other customers on this platform.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="lg:grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-1">
			  
				<div class="w-80 h-92 grid-col-1 flex flex-col p-4 mx-auto max-w-lg  bg-[#00161F] rounded-xl border border-blue-500 shadow shadow-gray-600 xl:p-8 text-white">
					<h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-medium text-blue-500">Starter</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-300">Try hiring overseas remote talent starting at a minimal cost.</p>
					<div class="flex justify-center items-baseline my-8">
						<span class="mr-2 text-3xl font-extrabold">$599</span>
						<span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">/month</span>
					</div>
					<div class="divider"></div> 
					<ul role="list" class="mb-8 space-y-4 text-left text-sm text-gray-300">
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
						  
							<svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
							<span>Metching with remote workers</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
						   
							<svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
							<span>Employer of Record(EOR) Service</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
							<svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
							<span>Payment service for salaries, social premiums, etc</span>
						</li>
					</ul>
				  
				</div>
			   
				<div class="w-80 h-92 grid-col-1 flex flex-col p-4 mx-auto max-w-lg bg-[#00161F] rounded-xl border border-orange-400 shadow shadow-gray-600 xl:p-8 text-white">
					<h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-medium text-orange-400">Standard</h3>
					<p class=" text-gray-300">Increase productivity with optimized 
						workspaces and basic HR management.</p>
					<div class="flex justify-center items-baseline my-8">
						<span class="mr-2 text-3xl font-extrabold">$799</span>
						<span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">/month</span>
					</div>
					<div class="divider"></div> 
					<ul role="list" class="mb-8 space-y-4 text-left text-sm text-gray-300">
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
						   
							<svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
							<span>All Basic Plan Services</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
						   
							<svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
							<span>Providing workspaces with fast, reliable connectivity and secure infrastructure</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
							
							<svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
							<span>Various HR management, such as attendance management</span>
						</li>
						
					  
					</ul>
				   
				</div>
				
				<div class="w-80 h-92 grid-col-1 flex flex-col p-4 mx-auto max-w-lg  bg-[#00161F] rounded-xl border border-violet-500 shadow shadow-gray-600 xl:p-8 text-white">
					<h3 class="mb-4 text-xl font-medium text-violet-500">Enterprise</h3>
					<p class="text-gray-300">Offer a range of additional support tailored to each corporate's needs.</p>
					<div class="flex justify-center items-baseline my-8">
						<span class="mr-2 text-3xl font-extrabold">Contact Us</span>
						<!-- <span class="text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">/month</span> -->
					</div>
					<div class="divider"></div> 
					<ul role="list" class="mb-8 space-y-4 text-left  text-sm text-gray-300">
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
						   
							<svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
							<span>Build an independent security environment</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
						   
							<svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
							<span>Private rooms and separate workspaces</span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
							
							<svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
							<span>Purchase and rental of necessary equipment on behalf of the company</span></span>
						</li>
						<li class="flex items-center space-x-3">
						   
							<svg class="flex-shrink-0 w-5 h-5 text-green-500 dark:text-green-400" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M16.707 5.293a1 1 0 010 1.414l-8 8a1 1 0 01-1.414 0l-4-4a1 1 0 011.414-1.414L8 12.586l7.293-7.293a1 1 0 011.414 0z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path></svg>
							<span>Various management support</span>
						</li>
					   
					</ul>
				   
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	  </section>

	<style>
		.CEO{
			width: 100%;
			background-image: url('../images/ceoimg.png');
		}
		.bgImg{
		  background-image: url('https://image.boxrox.com/2023/05/Laptop-sitting.jpg');
		
		background-size: cover;
		background-position: center;
		height: 40vh;
		border-bottom-left-radius: 100px; 
	  border-bottom-right-radius: 100px;
		
		}
		.overlay1 {
	  position: relative;
	  top: 0;
	  left: 0;
	  width: 100%;
	  height: 100%;
	  background-color:#0a4b5be2; /* Adjust the color and transparency as needed */
	  border-bottom-left-radius: 100px; 
	  border-bottom-right-radius: 100px;
	}
	
	.overlay1::after{
		content: "About Our Company";
		display: block; /* Ensures the content is on a new line */
	  font-style: italic; /* Example styling; you can adjust this as needed */
	  color: white; 
	  position: absolute;
	  font-size: 30px;
	 text-transform: uppercase;
	  top: 40%;
	  left: 50%;
	  transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
	  
	}
	.overlay2 {
	  position: relative;
	  top: 0;
	  left: 0;
	  width: 100%;
	  height: 100%;
	 
	  border-bottom-left-radius: 100px; 
	  border-bottom-right-radius: 100px;
	}
	</style>
</Base>